089-14b 'phags pa 'jam dpal la phyag 'tshal lo/ /oM bA kye te dzA ya/ oM bA kye Sha She swa/ oM bA kye khan dza ye/ oM bA kye niSh+Tha a/ oM bA kye ya na maHoM bA kye daM na maH/ 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi mtshan 'di nyid lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas pas mtshams med pa lnga'i las kyi sgrib pa thams cad 'byang ngo / /'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi mtshan rdzogs so// //
